essentials.cookie_long:
What are cookies?


Cookies are very small text files that are stored on your computer when you visit some websites.

Why does this website use cookies?


This website uses cookies to enhance user and administrator experience by letting users choose a preferred language and to enable edit possibilities for the website admin.

You can disable any cookies already stored on your computer, but these may stop this website from functioning properly. You can choose to disagree to cookie usage here. This will redirect you to the previous site you were on (or google.com if the previous site was this site) and delete all cookies made by this site.
